# QuantDeck needs NO API keys to run.
# The live FastAPI app sources everything (prices, fundamentals, news, analyst
# data) from Yahoo Finance via yfinance — no key, no rate-limit tier.

# NewsAPI — OPTIONAL. data/news.py falls back to yfinance headlines when unset.
# Not currently wired to any live endpoint (layers/deep_dive.py::run_deep_dive,
# its only caller, predates the FastAPI rewrite). Leave unset unless you're
# calling that function directly.
# NEWSAPI_KEY=your_key_here
